{
  "stem": "3277.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because the main dish was-- when you used to come back from the work, from the woods, they would give you 400 grams bread.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Which means 250 was maybe water and a little bit soup.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we couldn't make-- they, they would require from us to do more work, a lot of work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But who could do it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we used to get the minimum.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let's say those Russian fellows, they, they could withstand those, the terrible situations.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They could do anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they used to get more because they could do more work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were, you know, not used  to it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we used to get just 400 gram bread and a little soup.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You couldn't hold even a little piece for the next day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You, you, you ate, you, you eat the whole thing at once, and the soup.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Which means, in the morning, you had just the, just the water to drink.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And at work, the hunger used to come to you-- the hunger used to come to you and back, come and back.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was a terrible feeling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You were hungry, and you have nothing to put in your mouth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Sometimes we could find, under the snow-- because the summer is there three months.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We used to find something, let's say, some leaves or whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that's what we take, took into our mouth.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The leaves, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, we-- and it used to be a long way to go to the place where we used to cut-- from the barracks to the place where we used to cut those trees, it was a long way even to walk.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And some people, because no nutrition, at night, they used to get the-- they were blind.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as soon as got dark, they were blind.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
